Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's austere budget
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bwg1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Jan 1979
President Carter unveils austerity budget in bid to curb inflation. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.